{
  "stem": "2460.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The smell was terrible smell, but we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I never smelled before human flesh.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Never in my life.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I didn't know what is it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, during the day was grayish-- grayish black, grayish brownish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at night, we didn't saw the smoke, but we saw the fire from the chimneys.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So we got called roll call-- Appell.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And two-- two small German trucks-- army trucks-- came.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they parked front of the barrack with German Shepherds, few German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And all of a sudden Mengele showed up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know if he drove or he walked.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He just showed up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he started to talk German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I understand German.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was asking, who wants to work something with metal?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My father ordered me to leave, so I raised my hand.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But then, a lot of children raised their hands.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then he asked, who was already working with things-- with metal?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I thought, I was a mechanic since I was born.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I'm going to raise the hand.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "What can happen?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course I wasn't a mechanic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never worked in my life. 13 years old boy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I raised my hand, and I was in the front row.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were always standing friends together, because if they count and they cut us, they should be-- we should be always together.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So best friends, we always stayed together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And five, because I was the shortest-- I-- I still am-- I was standing in the front.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I decided to raise my hand.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my friends were angry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Miki, why are you doing that?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I told them, I have to leave here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I have to leave.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
